{"tid":2145703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《紐約時報》終止與《中國日報》合作　刪除新聞式廣告","createTime":"2020-08-08T07:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T08:08:38.000Z","uid":7542,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b86febb16647755842c2df91e0d302d9bd3e6740","tid":2145703,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報道，《紐約時報》已經將中國官方媒體《中國日報》刊登過的付費宣傳刪除；《華盛頓郵報》及英國《每日電訊報》亦已終止與《中國日報》合作。《紐約時報》發言人表示，今年初決定，停止接受國家媒體以新聞形式的廣告，包括《中國日報》，若果來自國家媒體其他形式的廣告，只要符合公司的廣告標準，亦會接受。報道表示，《中國日報》在十多年來，以插頁形式在《紐約時報》、《華盛頓郵報》和《華爾街日報》等海外主流媒體刊登廣告，宣傳中國政府的政策以及美化中國形象。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部資料顯示，自2016年11月至2020年4月間，已向美國媒體共支付1900多萬美元印刷費和廣告費。到今年4月為止，《中國日報》仍與《華爾街日報》和《外交政策》網站有資金往來。"},{"pid":"65b19b97a0600533a7b895024840858f5d211f72","tid":2145703,"uid":7542,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542569-20200808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542569-20200808.htm&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=30a924d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542569-20200808.htm&h=55883a25\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542569-20200808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dbe44262c1552a6b7b7a0bc7f4f0b06dbb1382aa","tid":2145703,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"b1a00eb6ddf64711bd5e400240dfc0306b58a201","tid":2145703,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d19766d0ecd354c93a3dc2910a4a46384bd153f2","tid":2145703,"uid":245409,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1a00eb6ddf64711bd5e400240dfc0306b58a201","tid":2145703,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score